  <brief_title>An Investigational Drug Study in Healthy Adult Volunteers in a Model of Insomnia (0928-007)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group, Multicenter Study of MK0928 in Healthy Adult Volunteers Participating in a 4-Hour Phase Advance Model of Transient Insomnia</official_title>
